s%20say%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Western%20trainers%2C%20the%20war%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20facing%20is%20unlike%20their%20own%20experiences.%20Ukraine%20is%20facing%20a%20major%20land%20war%20featuring%20trench%20warfare%20and%20artillery%20battles%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20World%20Wars%20mixed%20together%20with%20drone%20warfare%20unlike%20anything%20the%20world%20has%20seen%20before.%20The%20Ukrainians%20are%20battling%20a%20much%20larger%20adversary%20with%20key%20advantages%20in%20manpower%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%20that%20the%20dynamic%20is%20something%20instructors%20are%20aware%20of%20and%20act%20accordingly.%20He%20shared%20that%20Ukrainian%20commanders%20and%20sergeants%20often%20come%20from%20front-line%20units%20and%20%26quot%3Bknow%20very%20well%20how%20to%20clear%20a%20trench%20because%20they%20were%20doing%20it%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20the%20Ukrainians%20will%20push%20back%20on%20certain%20theories%20of%20war%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20didn't%20work%20when%20employed%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20militaries%20doing%20the%20training%20hold%20institutional%20credibility%20from%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20so%20%26quot%3Bwhatever%20the%20potential%20skepticism%20of%20experienced%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20on%20arrival%20here%2C%20their%20chain%20of%20command%2C%20their%20senior%20headquarters%20have%20decided%20that%20it's%20worth%20their%20while%20to%20come%20here%20and%20be%20trained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Men%20in%20camouflage%20gear%20and%20helmets%20and%20red%20sunglasses%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20a%20pale%20yellow%20brick%20wall%2C%20some%20of%20them%20with%20firearms%20raised%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6867d23a85e81483682d6902%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221357%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMembers%20of%20th