20key%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20upliftment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereached%20out%20to%20Pintu%2C%20he%20reiterated%20one%20thing%2C%20%E2%80%9CDreaming%20and%20working%20towards%20making%20a%20dream%20come%20true%20are%20two%20different%20things%20and%20I%20strive%20for%20the%20latter.%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20in%20actions%2C%20even%20when%20the%20circumstances%20are%20not%20in%20my%20favour.%20I%20believe%20that%20consistency%20and%20perseverance%20are%20keys%20to%20being%20successful%20and%20this%20success%20should%20be%20your%20merit%20%E2%80%94%20incomparable%20and%20self-motivating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFloods%20of%20change%3A%20Early%20writing%20days%20and%20struggles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20there%20were%20floods%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400833%2Fpayal-kumar-feed-the-souls-ngo-delhi-slums-education-skill-training-for-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadanmohantala%20slum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20back%20in%201989%2C%20if%20I%20recall%20correctly%20when%20I%20was%20in%20class%204.%20The%20water%20levels%20kept%20rising%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20vacate.%20We%20went%20to%20my%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20place%20to%20live%20for%20a%20while.%20I%20was%20an%20introvert%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20read%20something%2C%20and%20I%20used%20to%20live%20in%20my%20world%20of%20imagination.%20While%20I%20was%20taking%20a%20stroll%20outside%20the%20house%2C%20I%20found%20a%20book%20under%20a%20tree.%20It%20had%20dust%20on%20it%2C%20and%20the%20corners%20were%20damaged.%20This%20book%20was%20a%20collection%20of%20short%20stories%2C%20and%20I%20started%20reading%20them%2C%20one%20after%20the%20other.%20And%20that%20is%20when%20it%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20%3Cem%3Elekhak%20(writer)%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Esays%20Pintu%