0build%20a%20network%20of%20%26quot%3BAI-augmented%26quot%3B%20legal%20professionals%20who%20perform%20work%20for%20clients%2C%20particularly%20large%20enterprises%2C%20at%20a%20lower%20cost%20than%20Big%20Law%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20AI%20is%20the%20future%20of%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Omar%20Haroun%2C%20a%20former%20lawyer%20and%20Eudia's%20founder%20and%20chief%20executive.%20%26quot%3BNot%20in%20a%20dystopian%20way%2C%20but%20more%20augmented%20humans%20who%20are%20ready%20to%20completely%20change%20the%20work%20that's%20being%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20just%20under%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20Eudia%20already%20tops%20%2410%20million%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20across%20dozens%20of%20clients%20and%2C%20Haroun%20said%2C%20is%20on%20track%20to%20hit%20%2420%20million%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEudia%20launched%20with%20a%20bang.%20The%20startup%20emerged%20from%20stealth%20in%20February%20with%20%24105%20million%20in%20Series%20A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efunding%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-catalyst-hemant-taneja-redefine-venture-capital-baffling-industry-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20venture%20capital%20firms%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20had%20just%20one%20major%20condition%3A%20Eudia%20would%20get%20%2430%20million%20up%20front%20and%20the%20other%20%2475%20million%20as%20it%20found%20other%20companies%20to%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217fad6a7-2b96-41f5-9ef4-e16adbf4856d%5C%22%3EA%20different%20kind%20of%20investment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arrangement%20flips%20the%20script%20on%20the%20old%20corporate%20development%20playbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20young%20startups%20raise%20small%20amounts%20of%20venture%20capital%20to%20keep%20the%20lights%20on%20while%20they%20crank%20on%20building%20and%20selling%20a%20product%2C%20and%20then%20they%20raise%20bigger%20rounds%20of%20funding%20as%20their%20revenue%20scales.%20They%20might%20direct%20some%20of%20that%20investment%20toward%20buying%20other%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20to%20access%20new%20markets%2C%20secure%20talent%2C%20or%20take%20out%20a%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEudia%20benefits%20from%20a%20different%20strategy%20taking%20hold%20in%20startup%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%20is%20one%20of%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20venture%20firms%20role-playing%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mountain-capital-bringing-big-exits-back-healthcare-vc-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20firm%20and%20others%20have%20been%20buying%20mature%20businesses%20or%20consolidating%20multiple%20competitors%20into%20a%20single%20company.%20The%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20merged%20company%20can%20operate%20more%20efficiently%20by%20combining%20costs%20or%20applying%20technology%20to%20automate%20tasks%20and%20make%20more%20informed%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Eudia's%20case%2C%20General%20Catalyst%20trusted%20a%20battle-tested%20founder%20with%20its%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Eudia%2C%20Haroun%20started%20a%20company%20focused%20on%20surfacing%20sensitive%20information%20within%20large%20datasets%2C%20which%20proved%20particularly%20relevant%20in%20legal%20contexts.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20sold%20it%20to%20Relativity%2C%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20e-discovery%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaroun%20founded%20Eudia%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20legal%20teams%20deserve%20better%20than%20what%20most%20white-shoe%20law%20firms%20offer.%20Traditionally%2C%20companies%20would%20save%20their%20thorniest%20matters%20for%20their%20outside%20counsel%20to%20solve%2C%20Haroun%20said%2C%20but%20as%20the%20demands%20on%20legal%20teams%20have%20increased%2C%20they've%20sent%20more%20work%20(and%20money)%20out%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEudia%20aims%20to%20