block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Zabo%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F460332%2Fzabo-farming-in-nagaland-sustainable-solution-to-combat-monsoon-floods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZabo%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20practiced%20by%20the%20Chakhesang%20tribe%20in%20Kikr%C3%BCma%20village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Phek%20district%20of%20Nagaland.%20The%20word%20%E2%80%98Zabo%E2%80%99%20means%20%E2%80%98impounding%20water%E2%80%99%E2%80%94a%20fitting%20name%20for%20a%20system%20built%20around%20harvesting%20every%20drop%20of%20rainfall%20in%20a%20place%20where%20water%20can%20be%20scarce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERainwater%20is%20collected%20from%20forested%20hilltops%20and%20flows%20through%20a%20carefully%20built%20chain%20of%20desilting%20tanks%20that%20remove%20sediment.%20From%20there%2C%20it%20is%20stored%20in%20ponds%20lined%20to%20prevent%20seepage.%20The%20water%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20irrigate%20fields%E2%80%94it%20first%20passes%20through%20livestock%20enclosures%2C%20picking%20up%20natural%20manure%20along%20the%20way.%20When%20it%20finally%20reaches%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F401927%2Fpunjab-retired-ias-officer-kahan-singh-paddy-farming-new-approach-less-water-saves-money%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20rice%20fields%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20brings%20both%20moisture%20and%20nutrients%2C%20fertilising%20the%20land%20without%20a%20single%20drop%20of%20chemical%20input.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-07T191655.671_11zon-1751896208.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F202