thing%20we%20do%20is%20to%20derive%20complexity%20from%20the%20bean%20without%20adding%20anything.%20So%20these%20two%20or%20three%20farms%20we%20have%20identified%20as%20being%20interested%20enough%20in%20the%20single-farmer%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaitanya%20Muppala%2C%20CEO%20of%20Distinct%20Origins%20Private%20Limited%20(DOPL)%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20introduction%20of%20Manam%20Chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Manam%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%E2%80%98we%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98us%E2%80%99%20in%20Telugu.%20The%20brand%20is%20designed%20to%20delight%20chocolate%20lovers%20and%20offers%20signature%20tablets%2C%20bonbons%2C%20truffles%2C%20nama%2C%20barks%2C%20fudge%2C%20palettes%2C%20rochers%2C%20clusters%2C%20macarons%2C%20gianduja%2C%20spreads%2C%20cakes%2C%20pastries%2C%20and%20viennoiserie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201650px)%20100vw%2C%201650px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754.jpg%201650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c