0chocolates%2C%20the%20orange%2C%20the%20hazelnut%20%E2%80%94%20each%20one%20is%20so%20thoughtfully%20crafted.%20You%20can%20feel%20how%20rooted%20it%20is%20in%20India%2C%20not%20just%20in%20the%20flavours%2C%20but%20in%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20made%20and%20presented.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20to%20buy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Explore%20their%20full%20range%20of%20chocolates%20at%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manamchocolate.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20www.manamchocolate.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751882245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3362-min_11zon-1751876754.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D464967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Behind%20every%20Manam%20Chocolate%20bar%20is%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20a%20family%E2%80%99s%20story%2C%20and%20a%20field%20in%20West%20Godavari.%20By%20working%20directly%20with%20cocoa%20farmers%2C%20this%20brand%20is%20blending%20impact%20with%20indulgence%E2%80%94and%20showing%20the%20world%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20best%20chocolate%20grows%20from%20care%2C%20not%20just%20cacao.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Partho%20Burman%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F464967%2Findian-craft-chocolate-manam-west-godavari-world-chocolate-day%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Army%20Doctor%20%26amp%3B%20Railway%20Staff%20Safely%20Deliver%20Baby%20On%20Footover%20Bridge%20With%20Just%20A%20Pocket%20Knife%20%26amp%3B%20Hair%20Pins!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F431958%2Findian-railways-uniting-india-freedom-struggle-british%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%