Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20have%20that%20perception%20that%20you%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20travel.%20But%20I%20learned%20that%20if%20you%20have%20the%20will%2C%20people%20along%20the%20way%20will%20help%20you.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20be%20okay%20with%20the%20harsh%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20snowy%20slopes%20of%20Khardung%20La%20to%20the%20temples%20of%20Ujjain%2C%20Sonu%20has%20now%20traveled%20over%2014%2C000%20km%2C%20covering%2015%20states%20and%20three%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20chance%20encounter%20with%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20defining%20moments%20in%20Sonu%E2%80%99s%20journey%20came%20when%20he%20reached%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20after%20walking%20500%20km%20through%20mountainous%20terrain%20where%20cycles%20just%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20roll.%20There%2C%20he%20met%20renowned%20environmentalist%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%2C%20who%20inspired%20Aamir%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20character%20in%20%3Cem%3E3%20Idiots.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20impressed%20that%20I%20cycled%20all%20the%20way%20for%20the%20environment.%20He%20gifted%20me%20a%20new%20cycle%20in%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonu%20says%2C%20his%20eyes%20gleaming.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20meant%20so%20much%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20cycle%20but%20because%20someone%20I%20respected%20believed%20in%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20moment%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20validation%E2%80%94it%20was%20fuel.%20It%20inspired%20him%20to%20dream%20bigger%2C%20and%20go%20farther.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECharlie%3A%20The%20unplanned%20companion%20who%20stole%20hearts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharlie%20was%20just%20two%20months%20old%20when%20Sonu%20met%20her.%20Small%2C%20scrawny%2C%20and%20nearly%20run%20over%2C%20she%20seemed%20destined%20for%20a%20tragedy%20until%20Sonu%20stopped.%20%E2%80%9CI%20took%20her%20to%20my%20relatives%20in%20Rohini%20so%20she%20could%20recover.%20I%20thought%20I%E2%80%99d%20leave%20her%20there%E2%80%A6%20but%20then%20she%20started%20following%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20an%20impulsive%20act%20of%20kindness%20turned%20into%20a%20lifelong%20bond.%20Sonu%20attached%20a%20small%20carrier%20to%20his%20cycle%2C%20and%20Charlie%20took%20her%20seat%20like%20a%20queen%20of%20the%20road.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20smile%20and%20wave%20at%20us.%20Some%20message%20me%20on%20Instagram%20just%20to%20meet%20Charlie%20when%20I%20visit%20their%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185245.351-1751635502.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20has%20already%20travelled%20over%2014%2C000Km%20spread%20across%2015%20states.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185245.351-1751635502.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185245.351-1751635502-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185245.351-1751635502-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185245.351-1751635502-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185245.351-1751635502-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-462871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20has%20already%20travelled%20over%2014%2C000Km%20spread%20across%2015%20states.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeeding%20Charlie%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20been%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20carry%20a%202.5kg%20bag%20of%20dog%20food%20when%20she%20was%20a%20pup.%20Sometimes%2C%20she%20ate%20curd%20rice%2C%20rotis%2C%20and%20milk%E2%80%94never%20complained%20once.%20Shopkeepers%20gave%20me%20food%20for%20her%20free%20of%20cost%20after%20hearing%20our%20story.%E2%80%9D%20Now%20a%20healthy%20one-year-old%20weighing%2015%20kg%2C%20Charlie%20remains%20the%20heart%20of%20Sonu%E2%80%99s%20travels%E2%80%94and%20a%20quiet%2C%20steady%20source%20of%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20terrifying%20accident%20and%20Charlie%E2%80%99s%20heroism%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20their%20bond%20was%20tested%20like%20never%20before.%20While%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F101463%2Fcycle-the-sahara-anindya-mukherjee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecycling%20near%20a%20rural%20highway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20jeep%20hit%20Sonu%20and%20flung%20him%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road.%20He%20lost%20consciousness.%20Charlie%2C%20thankfully%20unharmed%2C%20ran%20400%20meters%20to%20the%20nearest%20dhaba%20for%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20jeep%20hit%20me.%20I%20blacked%20out.%20But%20Charlie%2C%20my%20brave%20girl%2C%20ran%20400%20meters%20to%20the%20nearest%20%3Cem%3Edhaba%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20get%20help.%20She%20brought%20people%20to%20me.%20They%20took%20me%20to%20a%20hospital.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20everything%2C%20but%20when%20I%20finally%20came%20back%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20jumping%20and%20licking%20my%20face.%20I%20broke%20down.%20That%20moment%E2%80%94that%20was%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3