ancy%20van%2C%20corporate%20sponsors%2C%20or%20expensive%20equipment.%20Just%20a%20cycle.%20A%20dog.%20A%20will.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20heart.%20Sonu%20puts%20it%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20humans%20are%20much%20more%20terrifying%20than%20any%20stray%20dog.%20Dogs%20just%20want%20love.%20Charlie%20never%20needed%20disciplining%E2%80%94she%20just%20needed%20someone%20to%20stay.%20And%20I%20stayed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20gear%20up%20for%20their%20next%20ride%20through%20the%20hills%20and%20valleys%20of%20the%20Northeast%2C%20Sonu%20and%20Charlie%20continue%20pedalling%20not%20just%20across%20India%2C%20but%20straight%20into%20people%E2%80%99s%20hearts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20help%20Sonu%20achieve%20his%20dream%20of%20opening%20his%20animal%20shelter%20in%20Bihar%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%2072004%2022273.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751639400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-04T185120.827-1751635404.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D462784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Sonu%20Raj%20met%20an%20injured%20stray%20puppy%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20she%20would%20change%20his%20life%20forever.%20Today%2C%20he%20and%20Charlie%20have%20cycled%20across%2015%20states%E2%80%94proving%20that%20love%2C%20grit%2C%20and%20compassion%20can%20take%20you%20anywhere.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F462784%2Fsonu-raj-charlie-cycle-journey-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2268%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Snow%20Leopards%20Are%20in%20Ladakh%20And%20Locals%20Helped%20Make%20It%20Happen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F425848%2Fbarley-ladakh-thukpa-tsetan-dorjay-of-siachen-naturals-empowering-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewindswept%20landscapes%20of%20Ladakh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20Himalayas%20cut%20across%20the%20sky%20and%20silence%20hangs%20heavy%20over%20snow-dusted%20valleys%2C%20a%20rare%20and%20mysterious%20predator%20still%20prowls.%20The%20snow%20leopard%2C%20often%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9Cghost%20of%20the%20mountains%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20an%20animal%20most%20people%20will%20never%20see.%20It%20moves%20silently%2C%20hidden%20by%20its%20thick%20camouflage%2C%20and%20has%20remained%20largely%20untracked%20for%20decades.%20But%20recent%20years%20have%20brought%20about%20a%20shift%2C%20not%20only%20in%20how%20we%20study%20these%20elusive%20cats%2C%20but%20in%20how%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20live%20alongside%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETracking%20the%20elusive%20predator%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20extensive%20snow%20leopard%20survey%20to%20date%2C%20reports%20%3Cem%3EMongabay%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards.%20That%20is%20nearly%2068%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20entire%20snow%20leopard%20population%2C%20of%20around%20718.%20This%20two-year%20study%2C%20covering%2059%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20the%20trans-Himalayan%20region%2C%20marked%20a%20major%20milestone%20for%20snow%20leopard%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20walked%20more%20than%206%2C000%20kilometres%2C%20recorded%20nearly%2010%2C000%20signs%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnow%20leopard%20presence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20installed%20956%20camera%20traps%20in%20high%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20low-density%20zones.%20These%20traps%20captured%20over%2026%2C000%20images.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20software%20called%20CaTRAT%2C%20trained%20specifically%20to%20recognise%20Himalayan%20wildlife%2C%20scientists%20identified%20individual%20snow%20leopards%20by%20the%20unique%20patterns%20on%20their%20foreheads%2C%20more%20reliable%20than%20side%20markings%2C%20which%20can%20be%20distorted%20by%20wind-ruffled%20fur.%20From%20126%20identified%20individuals%2C%20the%20team%20used%20spatial%20capture-recapture%20models%20to%20estimate%20a%20total%20population%20of%20477%20snow%20leopards%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bubo%20Birding%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-462647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELadakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bubo%20Birding%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20vision%20for%20coexistence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20these%20figures%20are%20impressive%2C%20the%20real%20success%20lies%20in%20what%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20effort%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345716%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-tsewang-namgail-himalayan-homestays-ladakh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20in%202003%20by%20mountaineer%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20and%20biologist%20Rodney%20Jackson.%20In%202013%2C%20after%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20passing%2C%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%20returned%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20he%20had%20been%20working%20as%20a%20wildlife%20biologist%2C%20to%20take%20over%20as%20director.%20His%20mission%20was%20to%20continue%20the%20work%20of%20building%20harmony%20between%20people%20and%20predators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20conservancy%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20initiatives%20is%20a%20livestock%20insurance%20scheme%20designed%20to%20reduce%20human-wildlife%20conflict%2C%20a%20common%20issue%20in%20pastoral%20communities.%20Each%20household%20contributes%20Rs%20400%20per%20year%20to%20a%20village%20fund.%20If%20a%20snow%20leopard%20kills%20livestock%2C%20the%20family%20is%20compensated%2C%20they%20receive%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20a%20small%20animal%20and%20Rs%207%2C000%20for%20a%20larger%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20alongside%20the%20ferocious%20predator%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20dream%20for%20the%20pastoral%20communities%20of%20Ladakh.%20But%20maintaining%20their%20livelihoods%20through%20schemes%20like%20this%20makes%20it%20possible.%20Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98Ri%20Gyancha%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETourism%20that%20gives%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20in%20attitude%20is%20partly%20due%20to%20the%20economic%20incentives%20linked%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20snow%20leopards.%20A%20major%20success%20story%20has%20been%20the%20Himalayan%20Homestay%20Programme%2C%20launched%20in%202001.%20It%20began%20with%20a%20simple%20idea%2C%20instead%20of%20building%20tourist%20camps%20that%20generate%20waste%2C%20why%20not%20have%20visitors%20stay%20in%20local%20homes%3F%20The%20conservancy%20surveyed%20villages%20and%20found%20strong%20support%20for%20the%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20centre%20of%20Ladakh's%20conservation%20effort%20is%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20in%202003%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Indiaspend%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2