.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20livestock%20and%20landscapes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservancy%20also%20supports%20the%20construction%20of%20predator-proof%20livestock%20enclosures%20using%20low-cost%20and%20locally%20sourced%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CVillagers%20provide%20the%20labour%20while%20SLC-IT%20provides%20wire%20mesh%2C%20doorframes%2C%20beams%2C%20and%20wooden%20poles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance.%20It%20preys%20on%20herbivores%20such%20as%20the%20Himalayan%20blue%20sheep%20and%20Asiatic%20ibex%2C%20keeping%20their%20populations%20in%20check%20and%20preventing%20overgrazing.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20herbivores%20feed%20on%20alpine%20pastures%20that%20grow%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslopes%20of%20the%20mountain%20ranges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20controlling%20the%20population%20of%20these%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20snow%20leopard%20gives%20the%20grasses%20and%20plants%20a%20chance%20to%20regenerate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Namgail%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wild%20Images%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T155514.706_11zon-1751624740-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-462677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20maintaining%20ecological%20balance%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wild%20Images%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20ecological%20balance%20has%20knock-on%20effects.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%20we%20are%20receiving%20more%20rain%20and%20less%20snow.%20As%20the%20rainwater%20flows%20down%20the%20slopes%2C%20the%20loose%20soil%20also%20goes%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20soil%20is%20loosened%20by%20the%20grazing%20activity%20of%20goats.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%20can%20help%20reduce%20such%20erosion%2C%20offering%20some%20protection%20against%20the%20increasing%20risk%20of%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThreats%20on%20the%20horizon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20growing%20threats.%20Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20a%20natural%20community%20of%20carnivores%2C%20including%20wolves%2C%20lynx%2C%20brown%20bears%2C%20foxes%2C%20and%20now%20feral%20dogs.%20But%20unlike%20the%20others%2C%20feral%20dogs%20are%20a%20man-made%20crisis.%20They%20pose%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20both%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20only%20worsen%20if%20left%20unchecked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20development%20also%20risks%20fragmenting%20important%20corridors%20that%20connect%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20snow%20leopards%20to%20populations%20across%20Tibet%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20Karakoram.%20Its%20distinct%20ecological%20and%20cultural%20identity%20calls%20for%20context-specific%20development.%20One-size-fits-all%20models%20from%20elsewhere%20are%20unlikely%20to%20work%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20model%20for%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouragingly%2C%20the%20survey%20aligns%20with%20international%20frameworks%20like%20PAWS%20(Population%20Assessment%20of%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Snow%20Leopards)%2C%20offering%20a%20model%20that%20can%20be%20replicated%20across%20the%20Himalayas.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20about%20tracking%20snow%20leopards%2C%20the%20same%20data%20and%20methods%20can%20be%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159407%2Fmaharashtra-hc-tiger-activists%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20other%20rare%20carnivores%3C%2Fa%3E%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T160257.690_11zon-1751625192.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20fondly%20called%20'Ri%20Gyancha'%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20SetMyTrip%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3